data.description: PRICE REDUCED! A quick commute to I-5 and JBLM will save you precious time to play in the neighborhood park or lounge in your own private backyard. The greenbelt behind you has lovely tall trees and foliage with morning bird songs to wake you. This versatile floor plan can adapt to a formal or casual lifestyle. The kitchen, dining, and living room share an open space that can morph to fit your needs. The dining area has room for a large formal table, buffet, and hutch or a desk and bookcase. The downstairs living area can be a TV room, or you can move the TV and video games upstairs into the loft. Retreat to the spacious primary suite with morning sun-facing windows for a quiet, peaceful respite.
